01:02:18.570 --> 01:02:20.600
PETE LEPAGE: Yeah, absolutely.

01:02:20.600 --> 01:02:23.890
So Brad, if you want to come
off screen-sharing and I'll

01:02:23.890 --> 01:02:27.410
